Municipality''' (''Ockelbo kommun'') is a [[Municipalities of Sweden|municipality]] in [[Gävleborg County]], in east central [[Sweden]]. Its seat is located in [[Ockelbo]]. The present municipality was formed in 1971 through the [[Amalgamation (politics)|amalgamation]] of "old" ''Ockelbo'' with ''Skog''. == Localities == * [[Lingbo]] * [[Ockelbo]] (seat) * [[Jädraås]] * [[Åmot, Sweden|Åmot]] ==References== {{reflist}} ==External links== *[http://www.ockelbo.se/ Ockelbo] - official site {{Gävleborg County}} {{Localities in Ockelbo Municipality}} {{coord|60|53|N|16|43|E|region:SE_type:adm2nd|display=title}} [[Category:Municipalities of Sweden]] [[Category:Municipalities of Gävleborg County]] {{Gävleborg-geo-stub}}
